    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Portable and collapsable frames, typically made of wood, designed to help wind/unwind skeins of yarn during the hand-spinning and weaving processes. This type of swift is equipped with various umbrella-like ribs that expand and/or fold in to accomodate variously sized yarn skeins.</Note_Text>
